description: Jetstream (Haroum ibn Sallah al-Rashid) is a fictional Moroccan mutant character that has appeared in various comic book series published by Marvel Comics.
name: Jetstream
powers: Concentrates thermo-kinetic energy beneath his feet to aid him in jet-like propulsion
Also has various technological components surgically inserted into his legs
Back which help to focus his abilities
